RAYNE v. WARDEN OF THE MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 42,

September Term, 1963.]

Decided December 6, 1963.

*591Before Brune, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Marbury and Sybert, JJ.

Per Curiam.

For the reasons for denying relief stated in the opinion of Judge Child in the Circuit Court for Worcester County, the application for leave to appeal is hereby denied.

Application denied.
